    "description": "<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/aac42ceb800fcf96c2881b1d25760e64.avif?t=1721990570\" width=348 height=166 /></span><br><strong>Cauldron Caution</strong> is a <strong>Point &amp; Click adventure centered on Card battles</strong> ! Fight against cartoony monsters with your <strong>Magic Creatures &amp; Ingredients</strong> ! Find <strong>hidden Booster Packs</strong> by exploring this wild world to improve your collection ! <strong>Meet quirky characters</strong> and <strong>solve diverse puzzles</strong> along the way !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/f1912fef1965e42742f278e7c506fdd0.poster.avif?t=1721990570\" width=368 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/f1912fef1965e42742f278e7c506fdd0.webm?t=1721990570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/f1912fef1965e42742f278e7c506fdd0.mp4?t=1721990570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SUMMON ASSISTANTS !</h2>Summon all sort of weird whimsical <strong>creatures</strong> ! From a clueless monkey to a cute pile of goo !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/32f964f62a4d14fcf8f2fe0dcaecd6a8.poster.avif?t=1721990570\" width=600 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/32f964f62a4d14fcf8f2fe0dcaecd6a8.webm?t=1721990570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/32f964f62a4d14fcf8f2fe0dcaecd6a8.mp4?t=1721990570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COOK INGREDIENTS!</h2>Make one weird soup by combining different <strong>magic ingredients</strong> together !<br>With a unique mechanic of chain reactions, Cauldron Caution offers lots of depth  !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/f0f3907f58fe3a438f74eaee855704f2.poster.avif?t=1721990570\" width=512 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/f0f3907f58fe3a438f74eaee855704f2.webm?t=1721990570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/f0f3907f58fe3a438f74eaee855704f2.mp4?t=1721990570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIGHT AGAINST A CHALLENGING AI !</h2>Play against a <strong>competent AI</strong> capable of using <strong>diverse strategies</strong> making each fight feels unique !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/d9af4630498c9a68e59c906c9c3d6478.poster.avif?t=1721990570\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/d9af4630498c9a68e59c906c9c3d6478.webm?t=1721990570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/d9af4630498c9a68e59c906c9c3d6478.mp4?t=1721990570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD YOUR DECK !</h2>Build a <strong>custom deck</strong> of your<strong> favorite creatures and ingredients</strong> from your ever-growing <strong>collection</strong> !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/1cfce4847373f297ffcf13d10702c6b9.poster.avif?t=1721990570\" width=600 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/1cfce4847373f297ffcf13d10702c6b9.webm?t=1721990570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/1cfce4847373f297ffcf13d10702c6b9.mp4?t=1721990570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DISCOVER FANTASY LANDSCAPES !</h2>Explore the world to find <strong>secrets</strong> such as hidden tickets to purchase new <strong>Booster Pack</strong> !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/f94c625819fde2f9057871e2fae52159.poster.avif?t=1721990570\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/f94c625819fde2f9057871e2fae52159.webm?t=1721990570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/f94c625819fde2f9057871e2fae52159.mp4?t=1721990570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FOLLOW A RICH NARRATIVE !</h2>Shyla the Shyder is a <strong>strange pink insect lady</strong> that only seems to fall from one predator to the next. Until one day, she finds the opportunity to <strong>fight back</strong> by summoning other <strong>creatures</strong> to her side and cooking dubious <strong>magic recipes</strong> with her trusty <strong>cauldron</strong> !<br><br>Cauldron Caution has a lot of charming NPCs to interact with, along with lots of bad jokes and crazy situations ! A very energetic adventure awaits !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/a7661842a2869655bac6ff55cf0187ed.poster.avif?t=1721990570\" width=512 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/a7661842a2869655bac6ff55cf0187ed.webm?t=1721990570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/a7661842a2869655bac6ff55cf0187ed.mp4?t=1721990570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SOLVE PUZZLES !</h2>Travel through numerous fantastic landscapes while solving puzzles to extend your collections of creatures and ingredients !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/47fa5af2c4adc98599a36db5894c754f.poster.avif?t=1721990570\" width=496 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/47fa5af2c4adc98599a36db5894c754f.webm?t=1721990570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023740/extras/47fa5af2c4adc98599a36db5894c754f.mp4?t=1721990570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ONLINE PvP MODE !</h2><strong>Challenge</strong> your friends and strangers online to intense <strong>duels</strong> !",
